A man has been ambushed by armed suspects and gunned down when he was opening his shop in Amanzimtoti. He was shot this morning while opening the store on Main Road in Doonside.KwaZulu-Natal police spokesperson, Thembeka Mbhele, says paramedics declared him dead at the scene. No arrests have been made.&#8220;Charges of murder and business robbery have been opened and are under investigation by SAPS. [We&#8217;re] still in the early stages of the investigation,&#8221; she said.!